reviewText: Saw them in concert about  year ago. They're somewhat older now, but they still sound great. Maybe even better. Very nice people as well.
wonderful... wish they would come out with a new cd
I bought this DVD for our granddaughter who is four and she dearly loves it.  (I think her mother does too!)
Excellent DVD.  Von Trapp Children have been singing for quite a few years and I remember the first time I saw them "in person"---and since then they have grown in their voices and their act.
